Frontend Architecture

A client from [neurlabs](http://neurlabs.com/) gave me a task to implement web frontend logic for their app, they had API and design ready. I can't describe particular details about the app idea, only technical solutions that I used during development.

The task was to display geo-tagged time-mapped data in a concise way. The data also has parameters that can be filtered upon, UI is supposed to provide appropriate data filters for user.

